<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="scarce-adj">scarce <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /skeəs/    美 /skers/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>不足的；缺乏的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In creative professions like art or advertising, openness to wild ideas are scarce and in demand.  
在像艺术或广告等创意行业中，稀缺并急需对疯狂想法的开明对待。</p><footer>2013 江苏</footer></div></div>